@startuml
title Farm Management System - State Diagram

[*] --> Login

state "Login" as Login
state MainArea
state MarketConditions
state MarketReport
state PestControlHelp
state Techniques
state SoilInfo
state WeatherInsights
state LabourAvailability
state UsingService
state Logout

Login --> MainArea : Successful login
MainArea --> MarketConditions : User selects market conditions
MarketConditions --> MarketReport : User chooses market report
MainArea --> PestControlHelp : User selects pest control help
PestControlHelp --> Techniques : User provides photo
Techniques --> [*] : User continues using service
SoilInfo --> SoilSuggestions : User enters soil information
WeatherInsights --> WeatherDetails : User provides location
LabourAvailability --> LabourDetails : User receives labour availability details
UsingService --> MainArea : User views results and continues
Logout --> [*] : User logs out
@enduml
